### Update README.md

```markdown
# CiteUrl.NET

.NET 9 library for parsing and hyperlinking legal citations.

## Features
- 130+ citation formats
- Thread-safe
- Streaming enumeration
- DI-friendly

## Installation
```bash
dotnet add package CiteUrl.Core
```

## Quick Start
```csharp
using CiteUrl.Core;

var citation = Citator.Cite("See 42 U.S.C. ยง 1983");
Console.WriteLine(citation?.Url);
```

## Advanced Usage
- Custom templates
- DI integration
- Streaming citations

## Attribution
C# port of Python [citeurl](https://github.com/raindrum/citeurl) by Simon Raindrum Sherred.

